snippet.title: Rover Rescue Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Teaser Trailer for the upcoming action strategy game, Rover Rescue! Rescue rovers across the solar system, hopping from planet to planet, whilst upgrading your Rescue Craft, battling the elements, and much more! for iOS, Windows, Mac and Linux. See www.roverrescuegame.com for more details.
